### Worktree Setup

Strategy: `{{ worktree.strategy }}` | Branch: `{{ worktree.default_branch }}` | Dir: `{{ worktree.layout_dir_name }}`

For full layout diagrams and setup commands, run:

```bash
ito agent instruction worktrees
